[Mod] A mod adding a way to give players interact. [rulesaccept]

This mod allows players to get interact if they didn't already get interact in this way before and slowly read the rules and accept them.
Of course the players are informed about this way to get interact automatically.
I used the [url=http://minetest.web1337.net/rules.php]rules of zegaton[/url] as default values.

[b]License:[/b] WTFPL (except the default rules)
[b]Download:[/b] [url=https://github.com/HybridDog/rulesaccept/archive/master.zip]zip[/url], [url=https://github.com/HybridDog/rulesaccept/archive/master.tar.gz]tar.gz[/url]
[b]github:[/b] [url=https://github.com/HybridDog/rulesaccept]rulesaccept[/url]

By default, so it looks like if the rules are viewed with interact.
[img]http://i.imgur.com/R9Aq3QM.jpg[/img]

