[Mod] Dogzilla131's DogBlocks mod edited [dogblocks]

I edited [url=https://forum.minetest.net/viewtopic.php?id=4566]Dogzilla131's DogBlocks mod[/url].
I changed the textures to be tileable and put the mod to github.

[b]Depends:[/b] wool, maybe default
[b]License:[/b] CC BY-SA for textures, rest WTFPL
[b]Download:[/b] [url=https://github.com/HybridDog/dogblocks/archive/master.zip]zip[/url], [url=https://github.com/HybridDog/dogblocks/archive/master.tar.gz]tar.gz[/url]
[b]github:[/b] [url=https://github.com/HybridDog/dogblocks]dogblocks[/url]

[img]http://i.imgur.com/9MT4Hzp.jpg[/img]
[img]http://i.imgur.com/D1Z3pvI.png[/img]

If you got ideas or found bugs, please tell them to me.

